Package zooproject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Enclosure
    Enclosure class is where Animals will live inside.
    Foodstore
    Food is held in a Foodstore class.
    PhysioZookeeper
    Extention of the Zookeeper Class PhysioZookeepers are able to call neckMassage() or bath() as addition to simple treatment
    PlayZookeeper
    Extention of the Zookeeper Class PlayZookeeper is able to call the watchAFilm(), playChase() or painting() methods on Animals which have that method.
    Zoo
    This class will have a number of Enclosures containing Animals, a collection of Zookeepers assigned to those enclosures, and will organise the day to day running of the zoo
    Zookeeper
    The Zookeeper comes in three different types.
    ZooProject
    Imitation of simplified life circle of the ZOO Each Zoo has Foodstore, some Enclosures.
